leads the rightist nationalist republican alliance or arena and 
took office june 1 after winning a presidential election 
his party has been linked to death squads that operated with 
near impunity in the wars early years and are blamed for most of 
its 70000 deaths 
the rebel farabundo marti liberation front in a radio 
broadcast tied the offensive to the oct 31 bombing of the 
national federation of salvadoran workers union hall in the 
