i think many things were done he said in an interview 
above all a descent into the bad things that characterize these 
times on this continent was avoided 
since he took office in march 1985 sanguinetti has watched 
neighboring brazil sink deep into foreign debt venezuela face 
riots argentina almost collapse under hyperinflation and peru 
bleed in a guerrilla insurgency 
uruguay with a population of just 29 million has not been 
free of the ills that plague its neighbors but never did problems 
